{"tid":1110073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解有一部分人會合理化老鼠安嘅行為","createTime":"2019-04-16T12:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T12:52:13.000Z","uid":203337,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1607f8c9144834a7b79ac60080c24983b5511f","tid":1110073,"uid":203337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"講到老鼠安對住個大波嫩口點忍 好正常<br />\n宜家係佢結咗婚走去偷食啊<br />\n就算結咗婚見到條𡃁妹正嘅就要食？<br />\n賓穎就更加唔駛講 背住馬明勾老鼠安<br />\n兩個一樣咁仆街 唔撚駛爭<br />\n你地班連登仔醒未啊？<br />\n仲喺度講話嘩 好淫好正<br />\n宜家係佢勾引有婦之夫啊<br />\n<br />\n根本呢兩個垃圾就係人人得而誅之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有伴侶仲偷食嘅人死全家"},{"pid":"4b7375f5f645c67badd888b934b17704fdd02b4b","tid":1110073,"uid":242444,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"因為男人都係狗黎<br />\n根本唔駛對男人咁好<br />\n當男人狗咁就得<br />\n因為遲早會出軌"},{"pid":"bfaad7db99e2aa9b6c62e79ff6150db17df01035","tid":1110073,"uid":135191,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登不嬲係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8491ac85fbecb03bcac50c0dfa3b4dfb4cff01e7","tid":1110073,"uid":203337,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"仲有平時有啲偷食post<br />\n男方偷食呢 當事人就好撚威<br />\n講到自己用咩手法去偷食<br />\n下面班連登仔就回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話男人識偷食好正常 完全合理化偷食<br />\n<br />\n而女方偷食呢 成個連登仔就搶住話人臭雞<br />\n瘋狂人身攻擊 幾乎冇連登仔會話偷食好正常<br />\n雙重標準到失衡<br />\n根本唔理男定女定不男不女 偷食就係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7ffaa4740e7b704573a1a45d3c0ac0bc0bffda","tid":1110073,"uid":167878,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"班人鳩up啫又認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e32efc0a20